&lt;span _mce_style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'MS PGothic';" style="mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;quot;MS PGothic&amp;quot;;"&gt;&lt;span _mce_style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;" style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: x-small;"&gt;Thomas M. Sterner 
is the author of &lt;strong _mce_style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;" style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;Practicing Mind: Developing Focus and 
Discipline in Your Life&lt;/strong&gt;. He serves as staff mental performance coach at 
Applecross Country Club, a Nicklaus design course in Downingtown PA, where he 
helps golfers of all levels improve their game. Visit him online at &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a _mce_href="http://www.thepracticingmind.com/" href="http://www.thepracticingmind.com/"&gt;&lt;span _mce_style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #0000ff; font-size: small;" style="color: blue; font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: x-small;"&gt;http://www.thepracticingmind.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span _mce_style="font-size: small;" style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span _mce_style="font-family: Times New Roman;" style="font-family: Times New Roman;"&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
